    "description": "这是一个回合制解谜游戏，你需要在被诅咒的岛上旅行，到达伯爵夫人的城堡来解除诅咒！探索岛屿，打败所有挡路的敌人，并解决阻碍你前往城堡的致命谜题！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/ee410086c2df0331ba853862ddd222b5.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/ee410086c2df0331ba853862ddd222b5.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/ee410086c2df0331ba853862ddd222b5.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作满满的解谜游戏</h2></h2>通过在房间里打败所有敌人、打开密封的门，并逃离该区域来解决谜题，但要注意岛上到处的陷阱！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/e6825911c5c471298b44743ce6c60396.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/e6825911c5c471298b44743ce6c60396.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/e6825911c5c471298b44743ce6c60396.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>由于邪恶的诅咒，每当你移动一次，你的剑就会变得更强大，但同时，你的每一次行动都会让你离死亡更近一步！<br><br>用你的魔法剑打败敌人可以刷新你的诅咒，防止剑吞噬你的灵魂！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/6fbb389546798adca98ba29a37098024.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/6fbb389546798adca98ba29a37098024.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/6fbb389546798adca98ba29a37098024.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.poster.avif?t=1745254866\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.webm?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200230/extras/94f51de130479f1b128141fec8ab686b.mp4?t=1745254866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在一个由危险和邪恶怪物统治的恐怖岛上开始你的旅程。<br></li><li>解决数百个致命的谜题。<br></li><li>快速的回合制移动，让你在做出致命的决定之前计划每一步。<br></li><li>在充满怪物和陷阱的八个可怕的区域中旅行！<br></li><li>遇到神秘的角色，有些是朋友，有些则不那么友好。<br></li><li>面对保护通往伯爵夫人城堡的挑战性守卫。<br></li><li>打败伯爵夫人并解除诅咒！</li></ul>",
